  "content": "## Rebuild Integration\n## Cargo Feature Gate\n\n# crates/corvia-inference/Cargo.toml\n[features]\ndefault = []\ncuda = [\"fastembed/cuda\"]  # Enables ONNX Runtime CUDA EP\n```\n\nNo Rust code changes required. `fastembed` automatically uses the CUDA execution provider when compiled with the feature and a GPU is available, falling back to CPU otherwise.\n",
